Usage:

To generate a pedigree file:
'java -Xmx6g -jar VCF2LR.jar -d <directory with .vcf formated files or a single .vcf file> -g <Genotype_Counts.txt> -o <output file name without suffix>'

To visualize the pedigree for a pedigree text file ped.txt:
'Rscript plot_pedigree.R <ped.txt>'

The output will be automaically created: ped.pdf

See:
https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5408770/
